7 An Act relating to revenue and taxation; amending 68
O.S. 2021, Sections 118, as amended by Section 35,
8 Chapter 310, O.S.L. 2023, 205.5, 220, 227, as last
amended by Section 4, Chapter 113, O.S.L. 2023,
9 228.1, 254, and 418 (68 O.S. Supp. 2024, Sections 118
and 227), which relate to state revenue
10 administration; modifying references; modifying
provisions related to certain revenue forecast;
11 modifying provisions related to information about
identity of certain taxpayers; modifying provisions
12 related to waiver or remission of interest and
penalty; modifying provisions related to claims for
13 refund of certain taxes; authorizing imposition of
fee with respect to reissuance of tax refunds;
